                "review": {
                    "reviewNum": 16783,
                    "reviewMergeOuterNum": 0,
                    "reviewNumText": "商品评价(16,783)",
                    "reviewMergeOuterNumText": "",
                    "reviewInfoList": [
                        {
                            "reviewId": 739302655429366100,
                            "comment": "对比过很多款，这款五层刀片的体验感直接拉满。渐进式切割，剃得干净又不伤肤，润滑条很贴心，湿剃干剃都舒服。每天几分钟搞定，剃完皮肤滑嫩不紧绷，质感和实用性都在线，值得入手。",
                            "descScore": 5,
                            "specs": "[{\"spec_key\":\"款式\",\"spec_value\":\"致顺4刀头\"}]",
                            "time": 1772622609,
                            "avatar": "https://avatar3.pddpic.com/a/Q0xBdVNkUlkrUFV6NE1xLzN5TDNaNytpQ0Z4cHlQWFVQZz09djA0-1667966061?imageMogr2/thumbnail/100x",
                            "name": "獭獭",
                            "anonymous": 0,
                            "orderNumText": "2次拼单该商品",
                            "mainType": 0,
                            "pxqFriendTag": false,
                            "isMyReview": false,
                            "commentTopRightTag": {
                                "reviewTagList": [
                                    {
                                        "type": 1,
                                        "txt": "2次拼单该商品",
                                        "color": "#9C9C9C",
                                        "font": 13
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "reviewId": 739720128431706500,
                            "comment": "锋利耐用，刮得干净利落，性价比超高。刀片贴合面部，顺滑不伤肤，剃须体验极佳。通用性强，适配多种刀架，是男士剃须的必备神器。",
                            "descScore": 5,
                            "specs": "[{\"spec_key\":\"款式\",\"spec_value\":\"致顺4刀头\"}]",
                            "time": 1772789537,
